column1: first enter the operation with two numbers (use a space to divide between digits and signs)
Press Enter and the first operation will be performed
then enter the sign and number through the space and press Enter and the calculator will work with the previous result
If you want to start new calculations
column2: enter the command "/calc reset" and start again
